Load ODS Layer Part 2 14

Use the Sort Transformation to get rid of any duplicate data:



Use Derived Column transformation to create three columns we will need to insert into the dictionary table.


***This is the code you will need to generate the ProcedureNumber Column

RTRIM(LTRIM(SUBSTRING(Procedure,1,FINDSTRING(Procedure + "-","-",1) - 1)))

Select OLE DB Destination which will be where we select our dictionary table.

Be sure to choose matching outputs and inputs.




Once completed, run the package and the dictionary table will be populated.


Repeat the above steps for each of the tables we have created for the ODS Layer.
